==Etymology==
From Latin '''[[monasterium]]''', ''monastery'', from '''[[monachus]]''', ''[[monk]]'', from Greek '''monachos''', ''single'' or ''alone'', + suffix '''[[-erium]]''' indicating a room or place

===Noun===
# place of residence for members of a religious community (especially [[monk]]s)

